# Working draft is root index.html (V3)

| Role | Path |
|------|------|
| HTML | `index.html` |
| Copy | `copy/COPY-v3.md` |
| Styles | `styles.css` (layout scoped to `.page-v2` until V3 CSS fork) |
| Images | `img/` |

## Frozen / archive (edit only when asked)

| Version | HTML | Copy |
|---------|------|------|
| V2 | `archive/v2/index.html` | `copy/COPY-v2.md` (frozen) |
| V1 | `archive/v1/index.html` | `copy/COPY-v1.md` |

## Redirects

- `/v3/` → `/` (current draft)
- `/v2/` → `/archive/v2/`
- `/v1/` → `/archive/v1/`

## Copy workflow (single source of truth)

1. Edit prose in `copy/COPY-v3.md` only — not in `index.html`.
2. Ask Cursor: **Apply all copy from copy/COPY-v3.md to index.html**
3. Preview by double-clicking `index.html`; push to GitHub when the live site should update.

## Conventions

- Spaced hyphen ` - ` in copy, not em dash
- Case study tags use middle dot ` · ` (e.g. Hard tech · Sensors)
